OL,3,CMan jailed after arson 'revenge
OL,4,Cattack' on man he believed was a
OL,5,Cpaedophile
OL,7,FA Leyland man who set fire to a house
OL,8,Fin a "revenge attack" after wrongly
OL,9,Fbelieving the occupant was a
OL,10,Fpaedophile has been jailed.
OL,12,FGareth Morgan, 45, admitted arson with
OL,13,Fintent to endanger life after starting
OL,14,Fa blaze outside the victim's home in
OL,15,FLeyland.
OL,17,FHe set fire to a bin, which spread to
OL,18,Fthe property's plastic front door and
OL,19,Fcaused extensive damage.
