OL,3,CMan jailed after arson 'revenge
OL,4,Cattack' on man he believed was a
OL,5,Cpaedophile
OL,7,FPreston Crown Court heard Morgan, of
OL,8,FCheetham Meadow, targeted the man
OL,9,Fafter seeing an online vigilante group
OL,10,Fclaim he had committed a sexual
OL,11,Foffence against a child.
OL,13,FHe later told a neighbour: "You will
OL,14,Fnever guess what I have done. I have
OL,15,Fjust put the door through of that
OL,16,Fnonce."
OL,18,FWhen he saw the same neighbour
OL,19,Fspeaking to police, he was seen
OL,20,Fmouthing: "shush, don't be a grass"
OL,21,Fbefore fleeing.
