OL,4,Cattack' on man he believed was a
OL,5,Cpaedophile
OL,7,FThe victim, who suffers from mobility
OL,8,Fissues and a heart condition,
OL,9,Fsustained burns to his nasal passage
OL,10,Fand a swollen voicebox, and was forced
OL,11,Fto relocate after suffering severe
OL,12,Fproperty damage.
OL,14,FIn a victim impact statement, he said:
OL,15,F"I have lived in Leyland all my life
OL,16,Fand have been forced to relocate due
OL,17,Fto this. Apart from my clothes, all my
OL,18,Fbelongings have been damaged."
