OL,5,Cpaedophile
OL,7,FMorgan, who has previous convictions
OL,8,Fmainly for drunk and disorderly
OL,9,Fbehaviour, told the court he regretted
OL,10,Fhis actions, describing them as
OL,11,F"reckless and impulsive".
OL,13,FHe also claimed he had "tried to move
OL,14,Fthe bin away from the building", but
OL,15,Fhis failure to call emergency services
OL,16,Fwas criticised.
