OL,3,CMan jailed after arson 'revenge
OL,4,Cattack' on man he believed was a
OL,5,Cpaedophile
OL,7,FJudge Robert Altham told him: "You
OL,8,Fleft the victim to his fate. He was
OL,9,Fthe only one who called emergency
OL,10,Fservices, by the time smoke was so
OL,11,Fthick he could not see his hands in
OL,12,Ffront of his face and had difficulty
OL,13,Fbreathing.
OL,15,F"There was thick black smoke. He had a
OL,16,Fsignificant swollen voicebox and burns
OL,17,Fto his nasal passage. He was admitted
OL,18,Fto intensive care for his injuries.
