OL,7,F"The victim has been forced to
OL,8,Frelocate as a result of your
OL,9,Foffending. There is a significant risk
OL,10,Fthat he could have died if he was
OL,11,Fasleep, he now struggles to sleep and
OL,12,Ffears a sense of concern."
OL,14,FMorgan was jailed for seven years and
OL,15,Fhanded a 12-year restraining order.
